title: #270 Fat Friend Lean In
description:
Folks, Mark & Joe thought they lost the first nine minutes of the pod but we left it in because it was gold. Anyway, Mark witnesses a classic subway fight while Joe is breakin' bottles and running into famous gays (not the kind you're thinking of). Check it out! 

Mark & Joe are doing a LIVE Tuesdays With Stories! at the Hollywood Improv TONIGHT, Tuesday, October 30th at 8:00! Get tickets here!
